## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of detailed historical records and the focus on Western Europe, particularly Italy. The experiences of women in other regions during the Renaissance may differ. Additionally, the sources primarily reflect the perspectives of historians and may not capture the full diversity of women's experiences during this period. Further research could explore more personal accounts and diaries from the era to provide a more comprehensive view.